    <head>BIOGRAPHICAL NOTE</head>
<p>Marjorie Knoll received her Bachelor of Science degree (1942) and Masters of Arts degree (1947) from the University of Nebraska and her Doctor of Philosophy degree (1954) from Cornell University.</p>  </bioghist>
